Happy 21st birthday AMSA-Indonesia!
*****
Never been that kind of organizational guy since I was in highschool. mungkin ini kalimat yang bisa menggambarkan gw banget sejak SMP sampai lulus SMA. Waktu awal-awal masuk ke fakultas kedokteran gw juga sama sekali ga ada pikiran buat ikut organisasi-organisasi tingat universitas. (Tried to be one in the early days but failed at the very beginningüòÇüòÇ) sampe waktu itu diberi kesempatan buat ikut magang AMSA lewat magang kelembagaan FK Undip, in that exact moment gw langsung jatuh cinta banget sama AMSA mengingat acara yang gw datengin waktu itu adalah kunjungan ke Komunitas Harapan Semarang (dari dulu sebenernya gw pengen banget ikut acara-acara yang langsung terjun ke community gini cuman gapernah berani buat ikut organisasi organisasi diluar sekolah) dan pada akhirnya gw meberanikan diri buat join di tenurenya kak @monicadestiani, dan yang gw gapernah nyangka banget kalo gw bakal deket sama banyak kakak-kakak kelas yang memperlakukan gw kayak temen ang udah kenal dari tahun lalu üò≠üò≠
.
Tapi mungkin awal awal gw masih kurang mengerti esensi dari AMSA sendiri karena masih clueless banget soal dunia perkuliahan dan masih memaksakan ikut organisasi ini itu sampai akhirnya ga sempat bagi waktu lagi buat AMSA. If I was asked whats my best moment di AMSA sebenernya bukan sebuah moment yang dirasakan di sebuah kegiatan AMSA, tapi kayak the moment of realization yang membuka mata kalo gw bisa jauh lebih berkembang di AMSA. .
Jadi awal dari cerita ini sebenarnya karena ekspektasi gw yang terlalu besar terhadap diri gw sendiri. Never imagined that I'll spend hours stumbling across instagram buat mengagumi orang-orang yang cuman gw kenal dari nama sampe ngeliat social-social medianya yang ga masuk akal lagi kayak issuu dan prezi üòÇ. Di titik itu juga gw sadar I can do much better than this!
.

[WORLD LUPUS DAY 2017]
Lupus is serious, life-altering, and potentially fatal disease that deserves more understanding and support. It is more pervasive and severe than people think, and has a devastating impact that the public doesn't realize. In fact, research shows that a staggering two-thirds of the public knows little or nothing about lupus. While lupus knows no boundaries, knowing all you can about lupus can help control its impact.
.
I, Andry Setiadharma, am joining this campaign in order to encourage all people of the world to join #InFlareNotDespair campaign to understand more about lupus and help those affected by lupus to get more attention. Whatever you decide to do on this day, make sure you help make the lives of those with lupus a little bit better.
.
Let‚Äôs make May purple and be a Victor!
.
#InFlareNotDespair
#WorldLupusDay2017

[WORLD HEALTH DAY 2017]
Depression can be effectively prevented and treated. The cheapest treatment you can get is a talking therapy.
Talking with people you trust can be a first step towards recovery from depression.

Considering that today is the World Health Day, We support this health campaign to fight against Depression by encouraging one another and support each other up, in order to build confidence in living life.

#LetsTalk
#EndDepressionTogether
